## Specifically for the top of the repo, ignore any IDE configuration files.
## The intent is that the subprojects should and will have IDE configuration
## files that *will not* be ignored by this rule.  If you copy this file into
## a project directory, remove this line.
.idea/**

*.log

## Local configuration file for Procfile based apps
.env

## Slightly better way to express than the shell glob
**/node_modules
**/bower_components

## Per https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206827587-How-to-manage-projects-under-Version-Control-Systems
## recommendation is to share "All the files under .idea directory in the
## project root except the workspace.xml and tasks.xml files which store
## user specific settings
**/.idea/workspace.xml
**/.idea/tasks.xml

